---
description: FastAPI conventions for llm-service
globs: "**/main.py,**/routers/**/*.py"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Keep `/llm` API contract stable and backward compatible.
- Use Pydantic request/response models for all route payloads.
- Return 422 for request validation errors and 502 for upstream/provider failures.
- Keep route handlers thin; business logic belongs in `llms/*`.
